    Returns

    We stand behind all of our products here at Duckbe. If you are not 100% satisfied with your order, we’re here to help. Please review the following guidelines regarding returns and cancellations.

    Return Address

    Room 201, Unit 1, Building 2, No. 43, Magangling Street, Baiyun District, Guangzhou, China.

    Returns & Exchanges – Within 90 Days of Purchase

    You may request a return or exchange within 90 days of the purchase date. All returns must be approved by our team before being sent back.

    Duckbe is responsible for return shipping costs in the following cases:

    • You received the wrong item

    • The item arrived damaged or defective

    • The personalization is incorrect due to our error

    • The product quality does not meet our standards (e.g., chipping, broken parts)

    In these situations, we will provide a replacement of equal or lesser value free of charge, and you do not need to pay the return shipping fee.

    Customer-Responsibility Return Shipping

    If the return is due to consumer reasons, the customer is responsible for the return shipping fee.
    The shipping fee varies depending on your address and the courier you choose.

    Customer-caused reasons include:

    • You changed your mind

    • You ordered the wrong item

    • You no longer want the product

    • Incorrect personalization provided by the customer

    Personalized (Custom-Made) Products

    Personalized items are custom-made and cannot be returned or exchanged unless there is a quality issue or an error on our part.

    Not Eligible for Return

    We cannot accept returns in the following situations:

    • The item has been used or is not in its original condition

    • The product was damaged due to misuse or improper handling

    • Returns sent without prior approval

    • Missing original packaging or tags

    • Items returned from a smoking environment

    Return Conditions

    • Items must be unused and in original packaging

    • Items must come from a smoke-free environment

    • Unauthorized returns will not be accepted
      Please contact our support team before sending any return. We will provide detailed instructions after reviewing your request.

    Refund Timeline

    • Refunds are issued within 3 business days after we receive and approve the returned items

    • Depending on your payment provider, refunds may take an additional 7–10 business days to appear

    • Refunds can only be issued to the original payment method

    Order Cancellation Policy

    Custom-Made Items

    • You may cancel within 24 hours after placing the order

    • After 24 hours, cancellation is no longer available as production will have begun

    Non-custom Items

    • Can be canceled anytime before shipment

    • Once shipped, the order cannot be canceled

    Need Help?

    If you have questions regarding returns or cancellations, please contact us at support@duckbe.com. We are always here to help.
